---
const faqs = [
  {
    question: 'Where does my code go?',
    answer:
      'To Anthropic — that is how Claude generates anything. Spark Commit itself makes no network requests. It passes your staged diff to the claude CLI on your machine, which sends it to Anthropic under your own account and their privacy policy. What Spark Commit does not do: run proxies, add telemetry, collect crash reports, or touch any server of its own.',
  },
  {
    question: 'Do I need a paid Claude account?',
    answer:
      'You need a working Claude CLI — any Anthropic plan under which `claude --version` runs in your terminal will work with Spark Commit. The extension adds no cost of its own.',
  },
  {
    question: 'Does it work in Cursor, VSCodium, or Windsurf?',
    answer:
      'It should work in any VS Code fork that supports the standard extension API and the built-in git extension. Not all combinations are explicitly tested — please open an issue if something breaks.',
  },
  {
    question: 'What about other AI providers?',
    answer:
      'Claude-only today, but the extension is designed to accept other CLIs in the future. Track the roadmap on GitHub.',
  },
  {
    question: 'How do I customise the commit style?',
    answer:
      'Open settings, search for Spark Commit and edit sparkCommit.prompt. The value is a free-form template — use {diff} where the staged diff should be interpolated. Conventional commits, emoji, a different language — all fair game.',
  },
];
---

<section class="border-t border-ink-900/10 dark:border-ink-50/10">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-20 lg:py-28">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Frequently asked</h2>

    <div class="mt-10 divide-y divide-ink-900/10 dark:divide-ink-50/10">
      {
        faqs.map((faq, index) => (
          <details class="faq-item group py-5" open={index === 0}>
            <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4 text-base font-medium text-ink-900 transition hover:text-sparkle dark:text-ink-50">
              <span>{faq.question}</span>
              <svg
                class="h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-ink-900/50 transition-transform duration-200 group-open:rotate-180 dark:text-ink-50/50"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                aria-hidden="true"
              >
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9" />
              </svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-base text-ink-900/75 dark:text-ink-50/75">{faq.answer}</p>
          </details>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }
</style>
